{
  "title": "StellarKraal Backend",
  "uid": "stellarkraal-backend",
  "schemaVersion": 38,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "title": "Request Rate (req/s)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total[1m])) by (route)",
          "legendFormat": "{{route}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "title": "Error Rate (5xx/s)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{status_code=~\"5..\"}[1m]))",
          "legendFormat": "5xx errors/s"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "title": "Latency Percentiles (p50 / p95 / p99)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 8, "w": 12, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.99, sum(rate(http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p99"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "title": "Active Connections",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 8, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "http_active_connections",
          "legendFormat": "active"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "title": "RPC Call Latency (p95)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 18, "y": 8, "w": 6, "h": 8 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(rpc_call_duration_seconds_bucket[5m])) by (le, operation))",
          "legendFormat": "{{operation}} p95"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "title": "DB Pool — Available Connections",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 16, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "db_pool_available",
          "legendFormat": "available"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "title": "DB Pool — Acquired Total",
      "type": "stat",
      "gridPos": { "x": 6, "y": 16, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "db_pool_acquired_total",
          "legendFormat": "acquired total"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "title": "DB Pool — Acquire Wait Latency (p95, ms)",
      "type": "timeseries",
      "gridPos": { "x": 12, "y": 16, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum(rate(db_pool_wait_ms_bucket[5m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p95 wait ms"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "title": "Alert Rules",
      "type": "text",
      "gridPos": { "x": 0, "y": 22, "w": 24, "h": 4 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "## Active Prometheus Alert Rules\n| Alert | Severity | Link |\n|---|---|---|\n| HighP99Latency | warning | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=HighP99Latency) |\n| HighErrorRate | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=HighErrorRate) |\n| DbPoolExhaustion | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=DbPoolExhaustion) |\n| RpcFailure | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=rpc-failure) |\n| RpcCircuitOpen | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=rpc-circuit-open) |\n| DbError | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=db-error) |\n| LiquidationFailure | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=liquidation-failure) |\n| 5xxSpike | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=5xx-spike) |\n| BackupFailure | critical | [View](d/stellarkraal-backend?var-alert=backup-failure) |"
      }
    }
  ]
}
